		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Chanting to draw upon the power contained in an igneous stone you carry, you make an upwards grasping gesture, and the earth surges upwards to grab creatures.</em></p><p><strong>Strength Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6 bludgeoning]] damage*, and target is &amp;reference[grappled]. Target rolls again at end of their turns: taking full damage on a failure or taking half damage and ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area is &amp;reference[difficultterrain].</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 bludgeoning]]{1d6} for each spell level above 2nd.</p>",
